data.name: hintServiceTimingResource1.Text
data.value:
The timing for the services must be specified in one of the following formats:

x sec(onds)

For example, 5 sec, or 5 seconds will indicate that the service runs every 5 seconds.
x min(utes)

For example, 5 min, or 5 minutes will indicate that the service runs every 5 minutes.
x day(s)
x day(s) HH:MM HH:MM HH:MM...

For example, 1 day 12:00 13:00, will indicate that the service runs every 1 day at 12pm and 1pm.
x week(s)
x week(s) HH:MM HH:MM HH:MM... Sun Mon Tue Wed Thu Fri Sat (being the day of the week)

For example, 1 week 0:00 04:00 Sat Sun, will indicate that the service runs every Saturday or Sunday at 12am and 4am.
x months(s)
x months(s) HH:MM HH:MM HH:MM... 1 2 3 4 (being the day of the month)

For example, 1 month 1:00 10:00 15 31, will indicate that the service runs every 15th and last day of the month at 1am and 11am.

data.name: hintServiceTimingResource2.Text
data.value:
服务的时间设置必须按照以下格式：

x sec(onds)

例如 5 sec 或 5 seconds 将设定服务每5秒钟运行一次。
x min(utes)

例如 5 min 或 5 minutes 将设定服务每5分钟运行一次。
x day(s)
x day(s) HH:MM HH:MM HH:MM...

例如 1 day 12:00 13:00 将设定服务在每天的中午12点和1点各运行一次。
x week(s)
x week(s) HH:MM HH:MM HH:MM... Sun Mon Tue Wed Thu Fri Sat (一周中每一天的英文名称缩写)

例如 1 week 0:00 04:00 Sat Sun 将设定服务在每周六和每周日的凌晨零点和凌晨四点运行。
x months(s)
x months(s) HH:MM HH:MM HH:MM... 1 2 3 4 (一个月中的第几天)

例如 1 month 1:00 10:00 15 31 将设定服务在每月15号和最后一天的凌晨一点和早上11点运行。
